## Tutorials and Resources

Resources for learning R programming and working with political science data.

### Congressional Data Guide

Comprehensive guide to working with congressional data in R:

[congressdata.joshuamccrain.com](http://congressdata.joshuamccrain.com/)

Topics covered:
- Congressional datasets and sources
- Data manipulation with tidyverse
- Regression discontinuity designs
- Working with legislative data
- Statistical models for political analysis

